    <briefdescription>
<para>The class <computeroutput><ref refid="classCGAL_1_1Surface__mesh__simplification_1_1LindstromTurk__placement" kindref="compound">LindstromTurk_placement</ref></computeroutput> provides a model for the <computeroutput><ref refid="classGetPlacement" kindref="compound">GetPlacement</ref></computeroutput> concept. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>It computes the placement, that is, the new position for the remaining vertex after a halfedge collapse, following the Lindstrom-Turk strategy (Section <ref refid="index_1SurfaceMeshSimplificationLindstromTurkStrategy" kindref="member">Lindstrom-Turk Cost and Placement Strategy</ref>).</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>TriangleMesh</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>is the type of surface mesh being simplified, and must be a model of the <computeroutput><ref refid="classMutableFaceGraph" kindref="compound" external="/home/runner/work/cgal-cn/cgal-cn/build_doc/doc_tags/BGL.tag">MutableFaceGraph</ref></computeroutput> and <computeroutput><ref refid="classHalfedgeListGraph" kindref="compound" external="/home/runner/work/cgal-cn/cgal-cn/build_doc/doc_tags/BGL.tag">HalfedgeListGraph</ref></computeroutput> concepts.</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<variablelist>
<varlistentry><term>Is model of</term></varlistentry>
